[Perhaps the root of the problem is that serotyping is not as specific as
PCR. Antibody tests may not distinguish reliably between closely related
hantaviruses, whereas I presume Heikki´s results are with the more specific
PCR. Or maybe Hantaan virus has sneaked around the southern end of the Ural
mountains. In any case, Alex´s lab has said it will make sera from the
outbreak available for testing - Mod.JW
